STR_ID_1202		 = 1202		-- He was trained to use the\nGreat Sword at a\nyoung age and excelled\nabove all. His fighting techniques provide\ngreat balance in speed and strength\nthat cannot be taken lightly.
STR_ID_1203		 = 1203		-- An ambitious individual who is very\nshort tempered. He may appeal\nsimple and ignorant but have enough\nself-respect where he cannot lose.
STR_ID_1204		 = 1204		-- Elsword’s sister was the Leader of the\nRed Knights. Since childhood, she\nrigorously trained him to become one\nof the Red Knights. However, she\nsoon left Elsword to pursue greater\nmissions for the Red Knights. Elsword\nwanted his sister to recognize him as\na strong warrior and soon joined the Kingdom’s El Search Party.\nEven so, his sister still did not acknowledge him to be strong\nenough. Elsword sets on a journey to become the leader of the\nstrongest El Search party in order to gain his sister’s trust.
