STR_ID_1209		 = 1209		-- She possesses strong magical powers and was\nonce known as a Great Magician. At the young\nage of 12, she traveled with her Grandfather\nto discover ancient magic ruins.\nHe was an old wise man and taught\nher all his secret magic arts as\nthey explored. During an excavation,\nshe discovered an ancient ring that\ndeviously absorbed and transferred her magic powers to\nsomeone else. In order to retrieve her powers back, she sets\noff on a journey to find the person who possesses her powers.
