STR_ID_1213		 = 1213		-- Rena, a fairy living in the forest’s\noutskirts of Elven mysteriously lost her\nsense to hear the spirits. This was because\nthe power of El that connected the Mortal and\nSpirit world was weakening. If continued, the\nMortal and Spirit world will be completely divided\nand causing all spirits in the Mortal world to\ndisappear. The prophecy reveals that the spirits\nare transformed into vicious spirits to protect the\nweakened EL. Rena felt the resonance of the El from\nthe tree of light and soon sets a journey to find it. She believes\nthat the tree of light will help her find the missing El powers.
STR_ID_1214		 = 1214		-- 24 years old
STR_ID_1215		 = 1215		-- Nasod Arm, Blade
STR_ID_1216		 = 1216		-- Half of his body was remodeled into a Nasod.\nHe uses his Nasod arm for strong attacks and\nhis swift blade skills for normal attacks.
STR_ID_1217		 = 1217		-- A very quiet individual who is\nvery cold and standoffish. The\nbetrayals from Velder Kingdom’s\nnobles have made him seek vengeance\nagainst humans.
STR_ID_1218		 = 1218		-- Raven, a fellow commoner from\nthe Kingdom of Velder worked hard to become\nthe Head Captain of the Crow Mercenary Knights.\nBeing a commoner in such a high ranked position\ncaused jealousy to arise from the nobles and they decided\nto frame him. After the rescue, Velder’s soldiers surrounded him,\nhis fiancee, and friends in the forest and slaughtered them.\nRaven awakens with devices attached all over his body in a Nasod\ncapsule. Reborn with a Nasod arm and a blade on the right-hand,\nhe fought unconsciously to destroy the kingdom he once protected.\nHe soon decides to join Elsword and his friends on a new\nlife adventure of finding the El Shards and to atone for his sins.
