STR_ID_1223		 = 1223		-- Eve, an upper-class Nasod, was once called\n‘The Little Queen of Nasods’ when Humans and\nNasod coexisted in Ancient Elrios. The times were\npeaceful and they worked side by side with their creators. Yet,\nprosperity never lasts as the power of El began to weaken and the\nNasod’s civilization was decaying without its power source. They\nsought help from the Humans but was denied and the war of\nNasod & Humans begun. Only a few ancient Nasods survived the\nwar and made it back into their preservation capsules.\nEve woke up to only find out that she was stranded alone in this\nnew present time. She decides to follow the red-haired boy and\nhis friends to find the El Shards and revive her race. After all, it was\nthe first time a boy said he wanted to be her friend.
