STR_ID_3910		 = 3910		-- Well-done! You’re a fast learner. Now try to dodge a box falling from the sky.\nIt won't be easy,  but I hope you can do it! Now hold on for 30 seconds.
STR_ID_3911		 = 3911		-- Now I think it's time for you to learn about a special ability. A special ability is an attack to give the worst damage to your enemy in the shortest time.
