STR_ID_4684		 = 4684		-- Henir: Velder
STR_ID_4685		 = 4685		-- Whoa! I've gotten pretty good, but that's too many, even for me!
STR_ID_4686		 = 4686		-- Where's the Velder Garrison!?\nWimps!
STR_ID_4687		 = 4687		--  There may be people in the castle.\nGotta save 'em, quick!
STR_ID_4688		 = 4688		-- The whole center of the capital's been taken over!\nI can faintly feel some kind of sneaky, spooky power; what could it be?
STR_ID_4689		 = 4689		-- Too many! Even I have to admit we're not ready to handle this!\nWhat do we do?
STR_ID_4690		 = 4690		-- It's not going to be an easy fight, but we have do our best!\nNo way am I going to let some crummy demons beat Aisha!
STR_ID_4691		 = 4691		-- The castle environs have been occupied!\nWhat could have happened?
STR_ID_4692		 = 4692		-- They are all over the city.\nI will do everything I can, but this will be a difficult struggle.
STR_ID_4693		 = 4693		-- Is there anyone still in the castle?\nThis way! We will protect you!
STR_ID_4694		 = 4694		-- They seem to have opened the gate from inside the capital and raided...\nA raid of this severity would have been difficult even for the Velder Garrison.
STR_ID_4695		 = 4695		-- I haven't felt this atmosphere of combat fields for a long time...\nNever really wanted to come back, though...
STR_ID_4696		 = 4696		-- Damn, how many more are in there?!...\nMust protect the external wall first!
STR_ID_4697		 = 4697		-- The Demons's capture of Velder is almost a cold fact.\nBut I must get in to find more about it.
STR_ID_4698		 = 4698		-- The Demons is living in a different dimension of this world.\nIt is hard to fight as we have little information...\nStill, it is lucky that we have dealt with them a little in Feita.
STR_ID_4699		 = 4699		-- The same energy changes as those in Feita detected.\nBut the gate larger than that in Feita was opened from inside.\nFeita must have been an experiment for dimension movement.
STR_ID_4700		 = 4700		-- Dark elves? I've heard about them…\nDarnit, don't run!
STR_ID_4701		 = 4701		-- Cut it out with all that dodging!\nStand and fight!
STR_ID_4702		 = 4702		-- Wait! Cowards!\nI'll get you!
STR_ID_4703		 = 4703		-- Demons working with Dark Elves--there's something you don't see every day.\nIt seems like the demons are really bent on taking over Velder!
STR_ID_4704		 = 4704		-- I heard that Dark Elves are really good in combat against Demons…\nSo what are they doing working together?
STR_ID_4705		 = 4705		-- Whew, that was a tough one!\nTheir eyes are nothing like Rena's. Creepy!
STR_ID_4706		 = 4706		-- A dark elf!\nHow is that cursed race here?!\nAre they allied with the demons?!\nThis is a great shame to my people!
STR_ID_4707		 = 4707		-- Dark elves are belligerent by nature…\nBut involving themselves in these wars? Surprising.
STR_ID_4708		 = 4708		-- Velder is greatly weakened and may fall…\nUnless we hurry!
STR_ID_4709		 = 4709		-- Dark Elf...?! Then they will communicate with men…!\nHey, stop there! Don't run away!
STR_ID_4710		 = 4710		-- Rational tactics... Not like intelligence of the general Demons.\nThis isn't an easy one.
STR_ID_4711		 = 4711		-- Being an elf, too, there is no grace of Rena's...\nI feel only heartlessness.
STR_ID_4712		 = 4712		-- Dark Elves Troop..! The troop has been trained hard and is a strong one. \nI am sure that this invasion has been prepared for a long time.
STR_ID_4713		 = 4713		-- Harmful to El, the source of our energy...\nThis one must be excluded.
STR_ID_4714		 = 4714		-- Elves have physical organs so ineffective for combats.\nLogically, it is hard to understand!...
STR_ID_4715		 = 4715		-- Let's go!
STR_ID_4716		 = 4716		-- Follow me!
