STR_ID_18438		 = 18438		-- I heard Adel is looking for a strong adventurer just like you! You should go see him!
STR_ID_18439		 = 18439		-- Welcome Pong. I have a plan to make you stronger Pong. Let's just say it's unleashing El's energy Pong.
STR_ID_18440		 = 18440		-- While we fought the Nasods, we also studied their technology. Recently, we have found ways to fuse Nasod technology and Alchemy pong.
STR_ID_18441		 = 18441		-- That's when we learned about a hero named Chung pong! From Echo pong!  Do you know Echo? I mean the cunning alchemist of Elder Village pong?!
STR_ID_18442		 = 18442		-- We want to create an engine that amplifies El's energy pong. If it fuses with Disfrozen, I'm sure it will produce enormous power.
