STR_ID_18447		 = 18447		-- Po Pong Pong Pong Pong! Almost fainted Pong!!!! Pong? What brings you here Echo Pong!
STR_ID_18448		 = 18448		-- Oh..El's energy doesn’t simply fuse this easily. King Nasod knows a lot about this. You might want to go and ask him.
