STR_ID_18450		 = 18450		-- That's Pong...exactly the problem, so that’s why this may not work Pong…
STR_ID_18451		 = 18451		-- King Nasod has a prototype device that we can use pong. But it is a very risky task pong. What you do think Chung? Do you think you have a chance pong?
STR_ID_18452		 = 18452		-- Wow! You really got it pong! Echo..Well! Echo...Now it's time for your alchemy pong!
STR_ID_18453		 = 18453		-- Let's see…let me try it…so don't interrupt. Err…it's not easy…
