STR_ID_18543		 = 18543		-- You are here rookie. This is the Ruben Village closest to the Ruben Forest. El Search Party is stationed here.
STR_ID_18544		 = 18544		-- We lost traces of Banthus' whereabouts around Ruben Forest. We will need some help from the villagers.
STR_ID_18545		 = 18545		-- Banthus is notorious around here as a bandit boss. If he showed up in Ruben Forest, he must be up to something.
STR_ID_18546		 = 18546		-- Outside the village by Lake Noahs, some bandits started to show up. Maybe they are related to Banthus.
STR_ID_18547		 = 18547		-- Perhaps you can find some clues from them?
STR_ID_18548		 = 18548		-- Hm…that thing you have… that is a bandit's order.
STR_ID_18549		 = 18549		-- Let me take a look. We can probably find out what Banthus is up to from it.
STR_ID_18550		 = 18550		-- The El placed on the top of the Tree of El is the treasured symbol of our village.
STR_ID_18551		 = 18551		-- Usually the El is protected by the forest spirits, but the rumor is that Banthus has a special necklace that can control forest spirits…
STR_ID_18552		 = 18552		-- Our El is in danger as suspected. Please get to Tree of El and protect it.
STR_ID_18553		 = 18553		-- Pant…pant… Darn those bandits and their cheap tactics! Arghh!
STR_ID_18554		 = 18554		-- Ey rookie! Let's head back to the village first. Since we lost them, we need to regroup to go after them.
STR_ID_18555		 = 18555		-- I heard from Lowe. They took the El… That's a big concern… We need to go after them right away, but there's another problem.
