STR_ID_24781		 = 24781		-- Hah! I'm finally coming next week! This is just a sample of how strong I am, so check me out!
STR_ID_24782		 = 24782		-- Hello adventurer! Nice to meet you, I'm a Night Watcher from the future to help you!
STR_ID_24783		 = 24783		-- Try this card to experience how powerful Night Watcher is! Godspeed~
STR_ID_24784		 = 24784		-- Hi! Your mission to save Ponggos has begun. Let's go and save the Ponggos all over the world!
STR_ID_24785		 = 24785		-- You found the Ponggos! I'll will support you with Mana Elixirs to help you with the rescue!
STR_ID_24786		 = 24786		-- Adventurer… We found Ponggos but Nasods are blocking the way. Please go help and get rid of them!
STR_ID_24787		 = 24787		-- You did it! The Nasods are gone now! Thanks to you we are closer to saving the Ponggos! Take this reward and please continue to help!
STR_ID_24788		 = 24788		-- We found out that King Nasod was behind the kidnapping of Ponggos! Please go defeat King Nasod! Then we can finally save the poor Ponggos.
STR_ID_24789		 = 24789		-- That evil King Nasod! I'm so happy that you were able to help save those poor Ponggos! Ponggos are very grateful as well. Here on behalf of Ponggos, take this.
STR_ID_24790		 = 24790		-- You decided to return back to base. I respect your decision. Well, on your way back, if you collect Ordinary Feathers and bring them back, we'll exchange them for you for a nice reward.
STR_ID_24791		 = 24791		-- They sure are ordinary feathers but once Ariel touches them, they will become special! So, what kind of accessory would you like to exchange them for?
STR_ID_24792		 = 24792		-- You decided to return back to base. I respect your decision. Well, on your way back, if you collect Ordinary Feathers and bring them back, we'll exchange them for you for a nice reward.
STR_ID_24793		 = 24793		-- They sure are ordinary feathers but once Ariel touches them, they will become special! So, what kind of accessory would you like to exchange them for?
STR_ID_24794		 = 24794		-- You decided to continue to help Ponggos. I respect your decision. Please continue to fight for those poor Ponggos and I'm sure they will never forget your heroic effort.
