STR_ID_25779		 = 25779		-- Great Job! This village sure has a lot of sand!
STR_ID_25780		 = 25780		-- Great Job! This village is so windy right? It is because Wind El lies underneath the village!
STR_ID_25781		 = 25781		-- Great Job! This village is in the middle of barren desert but grew tremendously as a transit trading town. You should definitely visit merchants!
STR_ID_25782		 = 25782		-- Great Job! This village is Sander! Wonder what the relationship is between Sander’s Rosean and Richian… Aren’t you curious too? Maybe you can find out in Sander. You’ll see it once you go past Hamel.
