STR_ID_26774		 = 26774		-- Ara Haan (Yama Raja)
STR_ID_26775		 = 26775		-- I've heard about the rumors…the rumors about the adventurer from the East with mysterious powers..Ara Haan..!
STR_ID_26776		 = 26776		-- When I was young, I too, traveled to the Fluone continent in search for adventure. Did you mention it was your hometown? I already heard what happened there.
STR_ID_26777		 = 26777		-- I've heard it has become a barren land of death, a lifeless land…I can imagine you have a heartbreaking survival story as the sole survivor from that tragedy.    
STR_ID_26778		 = 26778		-- Oh, I’m sorry! I didn’t mean to dig up past memories like that…I only want to…understand the pain you went through. I also wondered what was beneath your brave exterior.
STR_ID_26779		 = 26779		-- I reminds me of how I was once like before…If by chance, you are on the path to find ones responsible..I would like to help you in any way I can..
STR_ID_26780		 = 26780		-- There have been many thieves around Elder Village. Our land is being ransacked by swarming robbers! It's giving me a headache.
STR_ID_26781		 = 26781		-- Last time, we heard a bunch of thieves found a way underground in the waterways. Please assist us in driving them out of there.
STR_ID_26782		 = 26782		-- I know you have the hero in you to not ignore people in despair…I can trust you that you will do the right thing.
STR_ID_26783		 = 26783		-- This is a book I got from my travels in the Fluone continent. It is an old book with stained pages, a rather unique book.
STR_ID_26784		 = 26784		-- I haven’t had the chance to read it yet..but by looking at the pictures in the book, I can guess it’s something about martial arts. So I am sure you will be able to use it someway somehow. Why don’t you take a look?
STR_ID_26785		 = 26785		-- Ah…this book contains the technical principles of martial arts…!
STR_ID_26786		 = 26786		-- (Never did I know I would find secrets here…I think you can call this a rare coincidence…? But…it's nothing like the techniques of martial arts I learned as a Haan! Nevertheless, I think these techniques are too valuable to pass up.) 
STR_ID_26787		 = 26787		-- Thank you! Now I can become stronger to save my brother!
STR_ID_26788		 = 26788		-- Do you know a good place where I can train my martial arts..? I heard there is a place on the outskirts of Wally's Castle where strong enemies are.
STR_ID_26789		 = 26789		-- Gasp…But I need more training before to build up my confidence…Let’s go and ask Luichel if she knows a good place for training.
STR_ID_26790		 = 26790		-- What? Did you say, you know a good place to train? You truly have great willpower, don’t you? Hmm..Let me think of a good place to train for you.
STR_ID_26791		 = 26791		-- What do you think about Wally’s Castle in Elder? Wally no longer lives in the castle but his guards are still protecting it.
STR_ID_26792		 = 26792		-- There is a rumor that Lord Wally hid a powerful secret weapon. The castle is dangerous place but it can be perfect place for training!
STR_ID_26793		 = 26793		-- I'm glad you came back safely! Everyone has been talking about how you defeated the enemy so bravely… 
STR_ID_26794		 = 26794		-- From the furious battle people said they saw a Little Devil fighting. Hmmm...Little Devil..? Then, should I call you a Little Devil? I hope you can use your new training to accomplish your goals.
STR_ID_26795		 = 26795		-- I already heard a lot about your heroic bravery Pong. I'm in a bind myself and I came to request your help Pong.
STR_ID_26796		 = 26796		-- Your skills using spirit energy grows stronger with training Pong. The best training is earned when you fight against an even stronger enemy Pong.
STR_ID_26797		 = 26797		-- Ah…you are fantastic Pong. You are a master of martial arts. You have the superb movements. It is a incomparable state of excellence. 
STR_ID_26798		 = 26798		-- The soldiers that witnessed your fighting spirit on the battle field said they felt your commanding bravery. A bravery like no other, almost like a God of Hell.
STR_ID_26799		 = 26799		-- Therefore, I would like to name you, Yama Raja, meaning a God who rules Hell. Take your new name, go defeat the demon invaders and bring back your brother. 
STR_ID_26800		 = 26800		-- Defeat all the demons you can, and someday you will end up finding your brother as well…Until that day comes..!
STR_ID_26801		 = 26801		-- Thank you. With the vigorous training, I was able to better control my spirit energy.
STR_ID_26802		 = 26802		-- With this new power, I can at last defeat the demon invaders! And then..I know I will find my brother..!
STR_ID_26803		 = 26803		-- I heard you talked to Luichel. Luichel wants to thank you for your help.
STR_ID_26804		 = 26804		-- Luichel was once a adventurer herself. She has unique talents and can help you. Go and talk to her.
